	   <tr><td colspan=2>I believe you are correct except that delay has a small impact. In the course of a fight you will more than likely have instances where the primary swing has a positive dual wield check but your secondary is still in delay. In that case you would not receive the extra attack(s). I could be wrong and if so I'm sure I'll be &quot;corrected&quot;. Hehe<br>Regardless this weapon rocks in the secondary slot.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Dec&nbsp;&nbsp;1 21:24:57 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
